|##############################################################################
| TEXAS INSTRUMENTS INCORPORATED
| Standard Linear and Logic Group
| IBIS Model of SN74LVC1G373
| Single D-Type Latch with 3-State Output
| This file contains package information for the following:
|  SOT 6-pin (DBV) package as [Component] LVC1G373_DBV
|  SOT 6-pin (DCK) package as [Component] LVC1G373_DCK
|  DSBGA 6-pin (YEP) package as [Component] LVC1G373_YEP
|  DSBGA 6-pin (YZP) package as [Component] LVC1G373_YZP
| This device can be powered at the following Vccs:
|  1.8 volt Vcc
|  2.5 volt Vcc
|  3.3 volt Vcc
|  5 volt Vcc
| This file provides unique models under the [Model Selector] for each Vcc.
| For operation at a specific Vcc, select the appropriate model after each
| [Model Selector] keyword.
|##############################################################################
|
[IBIS Ver]      3.2
[Comment char]  |_char
[File Name]     sn74lvc1g373.ibs
[File Rev]      1.1 | x_die
[Date]          May 27, 2004 
[Source]        Data created from TI-SPICE simulations at TI-SLL.
[Notes]         The following is an IBIS list for the LVC1G373.
                Please contact sllibis@ti.com with questions and
                comments concerning SLL IBIS models.
                - FILE REV HISTORY
                - 1.2 YEP and YZP packages released on 05/27/04
                - Power-clamp data has been deleted since there is no
                  power-clamp diode in the device.  
                - Due to the fact that the Device is 5.5-V Input tolarent, 
                  the pulldown model has some Non-Monotonic Warnings.

